{
  "stem": "9156.8",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I have my papers here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that was very good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "London.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was at London at the labor desk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And constantly in contact with what's going on in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And among the papers that I told you I never opened-- I have them here-- he sent me material that he found in German newspapers that is the most dirty, racial against blacks that you can find.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I can show it to you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But just that-- I will never understand how any Jew can ever be against blacks, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just don't understand that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That we don't know that this is the same.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How long was he in Europe?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, all that time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was during all the blitz in London.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was, meanwhile, working at the child guidance clinic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I began to write, sometimes, about children in wartime and things like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I have to say that I finished my studies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- oh, people don't know how we lived when we were students.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I should say that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In one room with one girl in one large bed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it wasn't because we were lesbians, but we had no money to get into any other place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we lived on soups.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I mean, people should know that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To think that everything comes right like that, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You graduated, therefore, with a doctorate?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not, at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Master's degree.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A master's degree in social work in 1943.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I worked at the child guidance clinic, and I started a new program with groups, and that's the way I wrote a lot about it and all that kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, I have to do this very fast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Paul is still in the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
